'''''Fairy Tales: The Twins and the Taloden''''' was a planned young readers book to be written by [[John Whitman]] and illustrated by [[Kathy Mitchell]]. In it, the [[Solo twins]] would go to a museum on [[Tatooine/Legends|Tatooine]], to discover the Taloden, a snake-like enchanter who turned the museum curator's son into a [[Dewback/Legends|dewback]].

